                                <entry>
<para>specifies the system clock source. This parameter can be one of the following values: <itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para><link linkend="_group___r_c_c___system___clock___source_1gaaeeb699502e7d7a9f1b5d57fcf1f5095">RCC_SYSCLKSOURCE_HSI</link> HSI oscillator is used as system clock source. </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para><link linkend="_group___r_c_c___system___clock___source_1ga9116d0627e1e7f33c48e1357b9a35a1c">RCC_SYSCLKSOURCE_HSE</link> HSE oscillator is used as system clock source. </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para><link linkend="_group___r_c_c___system___clock___source_1ga5caf08ac71d7dd7e7b2e3e421606aca7">RCC_SYSCLKSOURCE_PLLCLK</link> PLL output is used as system clock source. </para>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para>
</entry>
